19 enum IntrinsicType {
20  INTR_NO_TYPE,
21  GATHER, SCATTER, PREFETCH, RDSEED, RDRAND, RDPMC, RDTSC, XTEST, ADX,

28 struct IntrinsicData {
29 
30  unsigned Id;
31  IntrinsicType Type;
32  unsigned Opc0;
33  unsigned Opc1;
34 
35  bool operator<(const IntrinsicData &RHS) const {
36  return Id < RHS.Id;
37  }
38  bool operator==(const IntrinsicData &RHS) const {
39  return RHS.Id == Id;
40  }
41 };

155 /*
156  * Find Intrinsic data by intrinsic ID
157  */
158 static const IntrinsicData* getIntrinsicWithChain(unsigned IntNo) {
159 
160  IntrinsicData IntrinsicToFind = {IntNo, INTR_NO_TYPE, 0, 0 };
161  const IntrinsicData *Data = std::lower_bound(std::begin(IntrinsicsWithChain),
162  std::end(IntrinsicsWithChain),
163  IntrinsicToFind);
164  if (Data != std::end(IntrinsicsWithChain) && *Data == IntrinsicToFind)
165  return Data;
166  return nullptr;
167 }

527 static const IntrinsicData* getIntrinsicWithoutChain(unsigned IntNo) {
528  IntrinsicData IntrinsicToFind = { IntNo, INTR_NO_TYPE, 0, 0 };
529  const IntrinsicData *Data = std::lower_bound(std::begin(IntrinsicsWithoutChain),
530  std::end(IntrinsicsWithoutChain),

533  return Data;
